query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from tag_question AS tq
inner join question AS q
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 0 AND q.score <= 1000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('math')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('brownian-motion',
'closed-form',
'convergence',
'definite-integrals',
'factoring',
'finite-groups',
'functional-equations',
'group-theory',
'linear-programming',
'matrices',
'measure-theory',
'physics',
'probability',
'real-numbers');
